function EggPhone:Update(pageChanged)

elseif self.Page == 1 then

end
end
function EggPhone:SetPage(pageNumber)

if pageChanged then
for _,connection in pairs(self.tempConnections) do
connection:Disconnect()
end
end
self:Update(pageChanged)
end
